##############################
# IBM ACCOUNT
##############################

IMAPAccount IBM
Host imap.linux.ibm.com
User mchauras
PassCmd "pass ibm/pass"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore Far-IBM
Account IBM

MaildirStore Near-IBM
Path ~/.mails/IBM/
Inbox ~/.mails/IBM/Inbox

Channel IBM
Far :Far-IBM:
Near :Near-IBM:
Patterns INBOX
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Sync All

##############################
# GMAIL ACCOUNT
##############################

IMAPAccount Gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User mkchauras@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass gmail/mkchauras"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore Far-Gmail
Account Gmail

MaildirStore Near-Gmail
Path ~/.mails/Gmail/
Inbox ~/.mails/Gmail/Inbox

Channel Gmail
Far :Far-Gmail:
Near :Near-Gmail:
Patterns INBOX
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Sync All

